reviewText: This dozen song compilation of "alternative" hits (Danzig doesn't fit this category) are as follows: Thunder Kiss 65-White Zombie, Everything Zen-Bush, Dreams-Cranberries, Universal Heartbeat-Juliana Hatfield, Can't Wait One Minute More-CIV, Hobo Humpin' Slobo Babe-Whale, I Touch Myself-The Divinyls, Cold Beverage-G. Love And Special Sauce, Blind-Korn, New Age Girl-Deadeye Dick, Backwater-Meat Puppets, and Until You Call On The Dark-Danzig. Runtime appx. 45 mins.
